title: 2 Bdrm/ 1 Bath At Skyline Heights Apartments

posting_body: ['960 Saint Francis Boulevard, Daly City, CA 94015', 'Upgrade your home and upgrade your life at Skyline Heights Apartments!', ' Ideally situated on beautifully maintained grounds in a lush, park-like setting, our luxury community offers Studio, One, and Two Bedroom apartment homes for rent in Daly City, California.', ' With easy access to the 280 and the Daly City BART Station, you can commute around the Bay Area with ease.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Quartz countertops in select units', 'Ceiling fans in select units', 'Expansive walk-in closets', 'Generous floor plans', 'Smart digital thermostat in select units', 'Double-pane windows', 'Community Features:', 'Three on-site laundry facilities', 'Pet park', 'Heated outdoor swimming pool', 'Sundeck', 'Gated community', 'Lush, park-like landscaping', 'Pet Policy: We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $500 pet deposit per animal.', 'Pet rent is $50 per month.', 'There is a weight limit of 35lbs per pet, and aggressive breeds are prohibited.', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Check out our virtual tour on our website at <URL>', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!', '*On select units, limited time offer*', '2Bedroom Floor Plan Virtual Tour:', 'https://youtu.be/XKZ7eib0psA', 'Amenity Virtual Tour:', '<URL>']
